---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Fragments
description: Mini-essays and compact reflections.
permalink: "/fragments.html"
---
<h1>fragments</h1>
<p class="secondary">: short mini-essays, compact observations, and small ideas about whatever crosses my mind.</p>
<br>
<section aria-labelledby="fragments">
{% for post in collections.fragments %}
<a href="{{ post.url }}" class="fragment-card-link">
<article class="fragment-card">
  <span class="fragment-number">#{{ collections.fragments | length - loop.index0 }}</span>
  <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
  <p class="subtitle">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
  <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
</article>
</a>
{% endfor %}
<p style="margin-left: 1rem;" class="secondary">More fragments added almost weekly.</p>
</section>
